&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400&quot;&gt;With over 13 years as a Senior Deputy District Attorney, Ambrosio E. Rodriguez is the criminal defense attorney you turn to when everything is on the line.&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400&quot;&gt;Successfully fighting criminal defense charges requires quick, strategic action. The period of time before the state attorney's office files formal charges is the best window for avoiding conviction or charges altogether.&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400&quot;&gt;If charges have already been filed, it is important to contact a criminal defense attorney as soon as possible. Before meeting with an attorney, try to gather as many relevant documents as possible, including:&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400&quot;&gt;Arrest warrants&lt;/span&gt; 
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400&quot;&gt;Police documentation of seized items&lt;/span&gt; 
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400&quot;&gt;Bail papers&lt;/span&gt; 
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400&quot;&gt;Dates and times of future court appearances&lt;/span&gt; 
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400&quot;&gt;Police reports (if possible to obtain)&lt;/span&gt; 
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400&quot;&gt;Records or prior arrests or convictions&lt;/span&gt; 
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400&quot;&gt;Navigating the criminal justice system alone can be extremely difficult and frustrating. Attorneys Rodriguez can use your documents and the details of your case to identify the ideal defense strategy for you.&lt;/span&gt;
