&lt;h2&gt;&lt;b&gt;Why Choose Zavodnick &amp;amp; Lasky Personal Injury Lawyers To Handle Your Accident Case in Philly?&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;b&gt;You Deserve Peace of Mind While You Recover&lt;/b&gt;
&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400&quot;&gt;You deserve the opportunity to focus on getting better. That's tough to do when you're also trying to figure out how to navigate an adversarial legal process and recover money for your injuries,&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400&quot;&gt;lost wages&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400&quot;&gt;, and suffering.&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400&quot;&gt;When you hire &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.zavodnicklaw.com/about-our-law-firm/&quot;&gt;Zavodnick &amp;amp; Lasky Personal Injury Lawyers&lt;/a&gt;, you give yourself the opportunity to focus exclusively on your physical and emotional well-being.&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400&quot;&gt;Our attorneys will handle every aspect of your personal injury claim from start to finish. We'll keep you informed and be there to answer your questions, but you won't have to worry about fighting for the money you deserve.&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400&quot;&gt;You focus all of your energy and attention on getting better. We've got you covered.&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;b&gt;You'll Face Pressure to Accept Less Than Your Case is Worth&lt;/b&gt;
&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400&quot;&gt;Attorney &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.zavodnicklaw.com/attorneys/ryan-zavodnick/&quot;&gt;Ryan Zavodnick&lt;/a&gt; and his legal team know the adversity and stress you'll face. We also know how to counter the moves in the insurance company's playbook. When we represent you, you can be confident that we'll force honest, transparent, and good-faith negotiations.&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400&quot;&gt;We'll bring in experts to ensure that we identify all of your damages and value them appropriately. We invest all the resources that matter, including the time and manpower needed to get our clients the result they deserve.&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;b&gt;You Have a Limited Amount of Time to File a Lawsuit&lt;/b&gt;
&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400&quot;&gt;In most situations, personal injury lawsuits in Philadelphia must be filed within&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400&quot;&gt;two years&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400&quot;&gt; of the date of injury. There are some exceptions to this rule, but they are few and far between. And, if you miss the deadline that applies, you'll be barred from seeking and recovering the compensation you rightfully deserve.&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;b&gt;When you hire our law firm, you'll have a team of experienced litigators in your corner.&lt;/b&gt;
&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400&quot;&gt;We'll handle every aspect of your case from start to finish &amp;#8211; beginning with:&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400&quot;&gt;Investigating the circumstances of your accident or injury&lt;/span&gt; 
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400&quot;&gt;Gathering evidence, such as accident reports, medical records, photographs, video footage, and eye-witness statements&lt;/span&gt; 
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400&quot;&gt;Determining causation, fault, and liability&lt;/span&gt; 
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400&quot;&gt;Consulting with experts in critical areas of your case, build a strategy, and identify and value your damages&lt;/span&gt; 
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400&quot;&gt;Preparing and submitting an insurance claim&lt;/span&gt; 
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400&quot;&gt;Negotiating with insurance providers on your behalf&lt;/span&gt; 
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400&quot;&gt;Filing a civil lawsuit in court, if necessary&lt;/span&gt; 
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400&quot;&gt;Exhausting all opportunities to gather information in the discovery process&lt;/span&gt; 
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400&quot;&gt;Sitting down with defendants and opposing counsel to negotiate a settlement&lt;/span&gt; 
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400&quot;&gt;Litigating your case at trial, if necessary.&lt;/span&gt; 
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400&quot;&gt;We will always approach your case as if we are certain it will require filing a lawsuit and going to trial. This means that we'll be prepared for anything that might happen along the way.&lt;/span&gt;
If you need help with your injury, &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.zavodnicklaw.com/contact-us/&quot;&gt;contact us today&lt;/a&gt; for help with the experienced personal injury attorneys at Zavodnick &amp;amp; Lasky Personal Injury Lawyers.

