&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400&quot;&gt;A child of divorce, Jennifer knows just how sensitive and complex family matters are. She says, &ldquo;We take great pride and are honored when people place their most challenging legal problems in our hands. They are trusting us with nothing less than their family's future.&rdquo; Jennifer treats every case with utmost compassion and is a fierce advocate for her clients.&nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;
