For more than three decades, Twyford Law Office has stood as a cornerstone of legal representation in Spokane, Washington. With offices strategically located in central Spokane and Bellevue, we diligently serve clients across the state, specializing in criminal law, family law, and divorce cases. Spearheading our practice is Attorney Julie A. Twyford, whose inaugural trial victory dates back to 1978, bringing unparalleled experience and expertise to our team.&lt;/p&gt;
Since that initial success, Julie has tirelessly represented numerous clients, excelling in both jury and non-jury trials, as well as negotiations. Her unwavering commitment to securing favorable outcomes has laid the foundation for our firm's legacy. Mark Cassell, our latest attorney, has swiftly established himself as a formidable force in family law, enhancing our range of services and client support.&lt;/p&gt;
What sets Twyford Law Office apart is our decades of combined legal experience, enabling us to provide assertive representation across diverse client needs. Revered within the legal community, we are known for handling high-value cases with precision and dedication, specializing in criminal defense, family law disputes, and divorce proceedings.&lt;/p&gt;
Beyond our adept courtroom performances, our hallmark is the compassionate, personalized service we deliver. We prioritize human connections, ensuring our clients feel understood and supported through every legal challenge. Our commitment transcends office hours &mdash; we are available 24/7 to provide guidance and support whenever our clients need us most.&lt;/p&gt;
At Twyford Law Office, trust is paramount. We cultivate relationships built on reliability, integrity, and a genuine desire to achieve the best possible outcomes for our clients. When seeking legal counsel in Spokane, rely on our seasoned team for unparalleled expertise, unwavering dedication, and compassionate representation tailored to your individual needs. Connect with us online or call (509) 361-6209 to embark on a journey toward legal success with a firm you can trust.&lt;/p&gt;

